<TITLE> Bashundhara boss sues Alo </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Mar 4 (bdnews24.com)Bashundhara Group chairman Ahmed Akbar Sobhan has filed a Tk 1000 crore defamation suit against Prothom Alo for a report published on Oct 12 that said "state machinery" was out to protect the company. Sobhan filed the case with a Dhaka court Thursday against Transcom Group chairman and Prothom Alo owner Latifur Rahman, editor and publisher Motiur Rahman, reporter Mizanur Rahman Khan, cartoonist Shishir Bhattacharya
